                <h6>SITUATION</h6>
                <p style="font-size:15px;">
                    Sociavi’s owner approached S&A Technologies with an idea for an automated communication system between elderly people in need and their caregivers/support.
                    The S&A Technologies team developed the initial system allowing Sociavi to successfully sell it to both private clients and institutions.
                    However, soon it turned out that the application needed an expansion and updated more robust technologies.
                </p>

                <h6>REQUIREMENTS</h6>
                <p style="font-size:15px;">
                    S&A Technologies was asked to convert the main components to a more robust and scalable platform and support it for the foreseeable future.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 career">


                <h6>CHALLENGES</h6>
                <p style="font-size:15px;">S&A was confronted with a set of challenges that needed to be overcome.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The existing functionality administrative and logging features.</li>
                    <li>Converting to new technologies would break the existing application. </li>
                    <li>Both design and development had to be financed through current sales.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 career">

                <h6>ACTIONS</h6>
                <p style="font-size:15px;">
                    We started our project by re-examining the client’s business model and finding out the company’s business goals.
                    Based on the new model, a series of tasks were established:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Short Term: Expand functionality and support the running application</li>
                    <li>Medium Term: Convert all components to a more robust and supportable platform</li>
                    <li>Long Term: Propose the right technologies and development steps to have a successful business in the future</li>
                </ul>
